      *@  업무처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.

      *@한도구분
      *@１－동일인신용공여한도
      *@２－동일차주신용공여한도
      *@３－거액여신신용공여한도
      *@４－자회사（개별）신용공여한도
      *@５－자회사（전체）신용공여한도
      *@６－대주주신용공여한도
           EVALUATE XDJL4031-I-LIMT-DSTCD
               WHEN CO-CHA-2
      *@            동일차주신용공여한도
                    PERFORM S3200-QJL0312-CALL-RTN
                       THRU S3200-QJL0312-CALL-EXT
               WHEN CO-CHA-3
      *@            거액여신신용공여한도
                    PERFORM S3300-QJL0313-CALL-RTN
                       THRU S3300-QJL0313-CALL-EXT
               WHEN OTHER
      *@            기타
                    PERFORM S3100-QJL0311-CALL-RTN
                       THRU S3100-QJL0311-CALL-EXT
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 기타
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-QJL0311-CALL-RTN.

      *@1.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL0311-IN
      *@1.2 호출변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL0311-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *@   기준년월일
           MOVE XDJL4031-I-BASE-YMD
             TO XQJL0311-I-BASE-YMD
      *@   한도구분
           MOVE XDJL4031-I-LIMT-DSTCD
             TO XQJL0311-I-LIMT-DSTCD
      *@1.3 프로그램 호출
           #DYSQLA QJL0311 XQJL0311-CA
      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@1.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   출력건수
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
             TO XDJL4031-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4031-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

150430*@       차주번호
               MOVE XQJL0311-O-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4031-O-BRWR-NO(WK-I)
      *@       채무자명
               MOVE XQJL0311-O-DBTRZ-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4031-O-DBTRZ-NAME(WK-I)
      *@       은행기준신용공여잔액
               COMPUTE XDJL4031-O-KB-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     = XQJL0311-O-KB-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     / 1000000
      *@       금감원기준신용공여잔액
               COMPUTE XDJL4031-O-FS-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     = XQJL0311-O-FS-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     / 1000000
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3100-QJL0311-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 동일차주신용공여한도
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3200-QJL0312-CALL-RTN.

      *@2.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL0312-IN
      *@2.2 호출변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
