      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@2.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   출력건수
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
             TO XDJL4031-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4031-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
150430*@       차주번호
               MOVE XQJL0313-O-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4031-O-BRWR-NO(WK-I)
      *@       채무자명
               MOVE XQJL0313-O-DBTRZ-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4031-O-DBTRZ-NAME(WK-I)
      *@       은행기준신용공여잔액
               COMPUTE XDJL4031-O-KB-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     = XQJL0313-O-KB-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     / 1000000
      *@       금감원기준신용공여잔액
               COMPUTE XDJL4031-O-FS-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     = XQJL0313-O-FS-GRCR-AMT(WK-I)
                     / 1000000
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3300-QJL0313-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

